(ii) Because the IHA was required to provide an opportunity for the applicant or family to submit evidence in accordance
with paragraphs (h) and (i) of this section; 
(iii) Because the IHA was required to wait for completion of INS verification of immigration status in accordance
with paragraph (l) of this section; 
(iv) Because the IHA was required to wait for completion of the INS appeal process provided in accordance with paragraph
(n) of this section; or 
(v) Because the IHA was required to provide an informal hearing in accordance with paragraph (o) of this section.



